snippet.title: Matchbox Emergency Patrol (CD-ROM Longplay #36)
snippet.description:
ORIGINAL DESCRIPTION:
A 3D game that I played the crap out of when I was younger. Although this game sucks. It's really not good. The physics are wonky and spacelike, the controls are clunky, and the graphics could be tons better, even on software mode. Oh well. Enjoy!

Developed by: Sandbox Studios
Published by:Mattel Interactive & THQ
(c) 2001 Mattel
